HEADWORD: Subjectivism
<hw>Sub*jec"tiv*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Metaph.)</fld> <def>Any philosophical doctrine which refers all
knowledge to, and founds it upon, any subjective states;
egoism.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Subjectivist</ent>⟦br⟧
